程序包 appliances

类 Appliance

java.lang.Object
appliances.Appliance
直接已知子类:
Dishwasher, Microwave, Refrigerator, Vacuum
public abstract class Appliance extends Object
The Appliance class is an abstract class of other specific devices. It contains common attributes itemNumber, brand, quantity, wattage, color and price.
从以下版本开始:
2024-09-19
